						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yic_aU1cmQ4">Congratulations, you survived your suicide</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yic_aU1cmQ4">Your sorry little heart still bipperty-bops from side to side</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yic_aU1cmQ4">You get to see another day, so head to the bay</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yic_aU1cmQ4">And maybe buy yourself an hour-long jet ski ride</a></em><br /> <em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yic_aU1cmQ4">Congratulations, you're back on the winning side</a></em></p> </div> <hr /> <p>Had this on my mind for a while. Nothing special, but I think its fun anyway.</p> <p>Valued critters include <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156835" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156835" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span></p> <p>And thank you for reading!</p> <hr /> <p>Did you like this? Wanna see more of my writing? You do?! Check out <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rtme-author">my author page</a>!</p> 
